# Socrata app token for datos.gov.co — optional for sample-mode/sequential pulls (you just get
# throttled public access), but REQUIRED for `make pull-full`/`make all MODE=full`: those run
# S1 and S2 concurrently, and without a token both would compete for the one small tokenless
# per-IP rate limit instead of actually going faster (pipeline.extract.pull refuses to run that
# combination without a token, see Makefile's pull-full).
# Register for free at https://www.datos.gov.co (account -> developer settings).
SOCRATA_APP_TOKEN=
